Package: isorunN2O
Type: Package
Title: Process IRMS runs of N2O analyses.
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: person("Sebastian", "Kopf", email = "sebastian.kopf@colorado.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package facilitates the reading, processing and visualization
